sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Host as Automation Host (Runner)
    participant UI as VCF9 AZ Placement UI<br/>(PowerShell / WPF)
    participant PCLI as PowerCLI
    participant VC as vCenter / vSphere API
    participant CSV as CSV Input Files
    participant OUT as Reports Folder<br/>(Run Logs)

    Host->>UI: Launch script<br/>STA relaunch if required
    UI->>UI: Initialize WPF UI<br/>Set runtime preferences
    UI->>OUT: Create run folder<br/>Text log + AZPlacement-Log.csv
    UI->>UI: Recheck prerequisites<br/>PowerShell 7, WPF, PowerCLI, VCF.PowerCLI
    Host->>UI: Enter vCenter, credentials,<br/>CSV paths, automation mode
    UI->>PCLI: Import VMware modules<br/>Set PowerCLI configuration
    PCLI->>VC: Connect-VIServer<br/>Primary + optional additional vCenters
    VC-->>PCLI: Connected VIServer sessions
    PCLI-->>UI: Connection status

    opt Create missing tag categories and tags
        UI->>CSV: Read Tags CSV
        CSV-->>UI: Category, TagName,<br/>ObjectTypes, optional vCenter/Server
        UI->>PCLI: Get/New-TagCategory<br/>Get/New-Tag
        PCLI->>VC: Create missing categories/tags
        VC-->>PCLI: Tag objects / status
        PCLI-->>UI: Bootstrap results
        UI->>OUT: Log tag bootstrap actions
    end

    UI->>CSV: Read Inventory Tags CSV
    CSV-->>UI: Inventory object rows<br/>Tag1..TagN + categories
    UI->>PCLI: Resolve inventory objects<br/>VMs, hosts, datastores, VDS
    PCLI->>VC: Query inventory + existing tags
    VC-->>PCLI: Inventory objects + tag state
    UI->>PCLI: New-TagAssignment when missing
    PCLI->>VC: Assign inventory tags
    VC-->>PCLI: Assignment status
    PCLI-->>UI: Tag assignment results
    UI->>OUT: Log inventory tag assignment actions

    alt DRS automation enabled
        UI->>CSV: Read Hosts CSV
        CSV-->>UI: ClusterName, HostRuleName,<br/>TagName, optional vCenter/Server
        UI->>PCLI: Resolve cluster + tagged hosts
        PCLI->>VC: Query hosts by tag within cluster
        VC-->>PCLI: Tagged host set
        UI->>PCLI: Create/update DRS host group
        PCLI->>VC: New/Set-DrsClusterGroup
        VC-->>PCLI: Host group status
        PCLI-->>UI: Host group results
        UI->>OUT: Log host group actions

        UI->>CSV: Read VMs CSV
        CSV-->>UI: ClusterName, VMRuleName,<br/>HostGroupName, TagName, RuleName/Type
        UI->>PCLI: Resolve cluster + tagged VMs
        PCLI->>VC: Query VMs by tag within cluster
        VC-->>PCLI: Tagged VM set
        UI->>PCLI: Create/update VM group
        PCLI->>VC: New/Set-DrsClusterGroup
        VC-->>PCLI: VM group status
        PCLI-->>UI: VM group results
        UI->>OUT: Log VM group actions

        UI->>PCLI: Create/update VM-to-host rule
        PCLI->>VC: New/Set-DrsVMHostRule
        VC-->>PCLI: Rule status
        PCLI-->>UI: Rule results
        UI->>OUT: Log affinity rule actions
    else Tag-only mode
        UI->>OUT: Log tag-only completion<br/>Skip host groups, VM groups, rules
    end

    UI->>OUT: Finalize text log<br/>Finalize AZPlacement-Log.csv
    Host->>OUT: Open reports folder
